title: WallArt v2.0.0 APK (Android) [HTD]
description:
Browse through stunning collection of wallpapers that can change the way your Android screen looks. Simple, quirky, colourful designs: custom made and hand picked.

Features:
50+ wallpapers and I'll keep adding on regular basis.
All the wallpapers are 2K. 
All the wallpapers are cloud based. 
You can save directly to your device.

All the Credits goes to Alex, Jahir and Sasi for dashboard and helping me out with problems.

Please note it might take to load all the wallpapers if your internet connection is slow.

What's in this version :
Live Wallpaper option added.
It's still in beta mode so you may expect bugs. After adding to Pool give it some time to sync and download. It should work fine.
Required Android O/S : 4.0+
